9th   [[Kim Campbell]] (Scottish)\n:20th   [[Jean Chr\u00e9tien]] (French)\n:21st   [[Paul Martin]] (Irish, French, Scottish)\n:22nd   [[Stephen Harper]] (English, Scottish)\n:23rd   [[Justin Trudeau]] (French, Scottish, English)\n{{col-end}}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Canada|Europe}}\n* [[European diaspora]]\n* [[M\u00e9tis people (Canada)]]\n* [[Ethnic origins of people in Canada]]\n* [[Eastern European Canadians]]\n* [[European Americans]]\n* [[Demographics of Canada]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book|author1=Bramadat, Paul|author2=David Seljak|title=Religion and Ethnicity in Canada|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VymssyK1Hs0C&pg=PA112|year=2009|publisher=University of Toronto Press|isbn=9781442610187}}\n* {{cite book|author1=Bramadat, Paul|author2=David Seljak|title=Christianity and Ethnicity in Canada|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z4HzXN4HQkQC&pg=PA247|year=2008|publisher=U of Toronto Press|page=247|isbn=9780802095848}}\n*{{cite book|last= Haig-Brown|first=C.|author2=Nock, D.A.|title=With Good Intentions: Euro-Canadian and Aboriginal Relations in Colonial Canada|publisher=UBC Press|year=2006|isbn=978-0-7748-1138-5|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vxFzgKZ0LKoC&dq=euro-canadian&printsec=frontcover}}\n* {{cite book|author=Kallen, Evelyn|title=Ethnicity and Human Rights in Canada: A Human Rights Perspective on Ethnicity, Racism, and Systemic Inequality|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xkqFAAAAMAAJ|year=2003|publisher=Oxford UP|isbn=9780195417425}}\n* Kralt, John. \"[http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_hb039/is_1_35/ai_n29045486/?tag=content;col1 Country of Birth of Parents And Ethnic Origins]  - A Comparison of Reporting Patterns in the 2001 Census,\"\n*{{cite book\n|first = Paul R| last = Magocsi\n|authorlink =\n|title =Encyclopedia of Canada's peoples\n|edition =\n|publisher =Society of Ontario, University of Toronto Press\n|location =\n|year =1999\n|isbn =978-0-8020-2938-6\n|url =https://