-797-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|date=October 6, 1989|accessdate=February 22, 2020|last=Benson|first=Sheila|title=Movie Review: Peck Shines as the 'Old Gringo'}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|1989\n|''[[Super Chief: The Life and Legacy of Earl Warren]]''\n|Narrator\n|Documentary\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1989/12/24/arts/judging-why-earl-warren-was-hailed-as-super-chief.html|work=The New York Times|date=December 24, 1989|accessdate=February 21, 2020|title=Judging Why Earl Warren Was Hailed as 'Super Chief'|last=Kaplan|first=David A.}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|1991\n|''[[Other People's Money]]''\n|{{sortname|Andrew|\"Jorgy\" Jorgenson|nolink=1}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{sfn|p=435|Haney|2005}}\n|-\n!scope=row|1991\n|''[[Cape Fear (1991 film)|Cape Fear]]''\n|{{sortname|Lee|Heller|nolink=1}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1991-11-13-ca-1188-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|title=Movie Review : Scorsese's Way With a BadFella|date=November 13, 1991|accessdate=February 22, 2020|last=Turan|first=Kenneth}}</ref> \n|-\n!scope=row|1994\n|''{{sort|Hunt|The Hunt for Adolf Eichmann}}''\n|Narrator\n|Documentary\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1994-10-03-ca-45907-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|title='Newland' to Open Israeli Film Series|last=Thomas|first=Kevin|date=October 3, 1994|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|1995\n|''Wild Bill: Hollywood Maverick''\n|Himself\n|Documentary\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/wild-bill-hollywood-maverick-1200444015/|work=Variety|title=Wild Bill: Hollywood Maverick|last=Elley|first=Derek|date=December 17, 1995|accessdate=February 22, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|1999\n|''{{sortname|The|Art of Norton Simon|nolink=1}}''\n|Narrator\n|Documentary short film\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cit